{"title":"送行","authors":["冰夫"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":8,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"送行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰夫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瀑跃高崖如鼓响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风摇白杨似锣鸣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男女老幼过山洼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢送铁柱去参军。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送过三里桃花峪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送到五里青松岭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满岭松枝沙沙响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姥姥细语嘱外孙："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“柱儿，你娘为革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热血染透青松林。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你带棵松苗上海岛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命部队去扎根。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记住家乡沂蒙山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要学青松不畏寒！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁柱健步走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支书紧相跟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送过七里赤龙坡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送到九里雁翅林。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹波涌水磨响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿柳红杏笑相迎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“铁柱，前年修水库，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你带民兵劈山岭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗珠滚滚岩石碎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梯田层层麦苗青。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送你一壶家乡水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记住你是沂蒙山里人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要学大雁振翅飞千里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹雨打不稍停。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青松岭啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雁翅林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几里家乡道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少霜和尘；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲人送别一席话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"句句记在心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沂蒙山上千条路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过父辈一代人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁柱跟着脚印走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出沂蒙，高歌进军营。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}